    "Frequently Asked Questions": "Pertanyaan yang Sering Diajukan",
    "Is there an initial setup fee?": "Apakah ada biaya setup awal?",
    "No! You can register and use our platform right away without any setup fee. All plans include a free 14-day trial.": "Tidak ada! Anda bisa langsung mendaftar dan menggunakan platform kami tanpa biaya setup. Semua paket termasuk trial gratis selama 14 hari.",
    "How secure is our school data?": "Bagaimana keamanan data sekolah kami?",
    "Your data is encrypted end-to-end and stored on ISO 27001 certified servers. We perform automatic daily backups and have a disaster recovery plan.": "Data Anda dienkripsi end-to-end dan disimpan di server yang tersertifikasi ISO 27001. Kami melakukan backup otomatis setiap hari dan memiliki disaster recovery plan.",
    "Can we import data from the old system?": "Apakah bisa import data dari sistem lama?",
    "Of course! We provide data import via Excel/CSV files. Our team is also ready to help with data migration from your old system.": "Tentu! Kami menyediakan fitur import data melalui file Excel/CSV. Tim kami juga siap membantu proses migrasi data dari sistem lama Anda.",
    "How long is the implementation process?": "Berapa lama proses implementasi?",
    "For Starter and Professional plans, schools can be operational in 1-3 days. For Enterprise with customization, it usually takes 1-2 weeks.": "Untuk paket Starter dan Professional, sekolah bisa langsung beroperasi dalam 1-3 hari. Untuk Enterprise dengan kustomisasi, biasanya membutuhkan 1-2 minggu.",
    "Is there training for teachers and staff?": "Apakah ada pelatihan untuk guru dan staff?",
    "Yes! We provide free online training through video tutorials and webinars. For Enterprise plans, we provide on-site training.": "Ya! Kami menyediakan pelatihan online gratis melalui video tutorial dan webinar. Untuk paket Enterprise, kami menyediakan pelatihan on-site.",
    "What if we want to unsubscribe?": "Bagaimana jika ingin berhenti berlangganan?",
    "You can cancel anytime without penalty. Your data will be stored for 30 days and can be exported before deletion.": "Anda bisa berhenti kapan saja tanpa penalti. Data Anda akan tetap tersimpan selama 30 hari dan bisa diekspor sebelum dihapus.",
    "Start Managing Your School Now": "Mulai Kelola Sekolah Anda Sekarang",
